# Basic computation

## complete command
```{r}
1+2
```
## incomplete command
```{r}
1+

```
* complete by placing 2
* dropping it press `Esc`

# Group Exercise t using R
```{r}
x <- 52.5
u <- 50
s <- 3.5
n <- 30
t <- (x-u)/(s/sqrt(n))
t
```
# Vectors
```{r}
x = c(1,2,3)
y = c(5,6,7,8)
z = c(x, y) # combining two vectors
a = c(1:20)
a = c(20:1) # will do it backwards
a = 1:20 # will make a data series
```

